<pre class="language-csharp"><code class="language-csharp">public int ClosestLine;</code></pre>

<h2 id="remarks">Remarks</h2><p>If the point is directly over
a line this value will be the same as the <code>OverLine</code> property.  If the point is
above the first line, this value will be 0.  If the point is below the last
line this value will be the index of the last line.</p>

